你知道嘛，我也要在派对上这么做

173
00:11:28,45 --> 00:11:31,04
- Know what I like most? - What?
- 知道我最喜欢他哪一点? - 哪一点？

174
00:11:31,79 --> 00:11:35,12
The way he makes me feel about myself.
他改变我看待自己的方式

175
00:11:57,31 --> 00:11:59,37
How was the game?
比赛如何?

176
00:11:59,58 --> 00:12:01,05
Well..
怎么说呢

177
00:12:01,25 --> 00:12:03,77
We won!
我们赢啦

178
00:12:04,69 --> 00:12:07,45
Fantastic! Question. How is that possible?
神奇!提问：这怎么可能呢？

179
00:12:08,49 --> 00:12:10,75
- Alan. - He was unbelievable!
- 亚伦 - 他真是太不可思议了

180
00:12:10,96 --> 00:12:14,66
Like the cartoon where Bugs Bunny plays every position.
他就像兔宝宝一样守每个位置

181
00:12:14,86 --> 00:12:19,09
It was first base,Alan. Second base,Alan..
 但我们有一垒手亚伦、二垒手亚伦…

182
00:12:22,50 --> 00:12:25,34
It was like he made us into a team.
他使我们形成一个团队

183
00:12:25,54 --> 00:12:30,48
We sure showed those Hasidic jewelers a thing or two about softball.
对，我们让对手见识到什么叫垒球

184
00:12:31,58 --> 00:12:33,44
Can I ask a question?
能问你们一个问题吗?

185
00:12:33,65 --> 00:12:35,98
Do you think Alan is sometimes..
你是否曾感觉亚伦有时…

186
00:12:36,18 --> 00:12:37,17
What?
有时怎样?

187
00:12:37,38 --> 00:12:40,01
I don't know. A little too "Alan"?
我说不上来，太亚伦了

188
00:12:40,22 --> 00:12:43,75
Oh,no. Not possible. You can never be too "Alan."
不，不可能 你不可能太过於“亚伦”

189
00:12:43,96 --> 00:12:48,76
It's his innate "Alan-ness" that we adore.
没错我们欣赏的是亚伦的内在

190
00:12:48,96 --> 00:12:51,96
I,personally,could have a gallon of Alan.
我…一个人可以喝下一加仑的亚伦

191
00:12:59,41 --> 00:13:01,93
- Hey,Lizzy. - Hey,weird girl.
- 嘿,露西 - 嘿,古怪女孩

192
00:13:02,81 --> 00:13:05,28
- I brought alphabet soup. - Pick out the vowels?
- 我带字母汤来给你 - 你挑出有元音了吗?

193
00:13:05,48 --> 00:13:08,45
I left in the Y's. Because,"sometimes Y."
但我把“Y”留下来了 因为有时你会用的上,“Why”(音同Y)

194
00:13:09,82 --> 00:13:12,18
- And something else. - Saltines?
- 我还带了其他东西给你 - 咸饼干吗?

195
00:13:12,39 --> 00:13:14,72
No,$1000 and a football phone.
但愿你喜欢一千元和足球电话

196
00:13:15,42 --> 00:13:16,72
What?
什么?

197
00:13:17,73 --> 00:13:19,39
Oh,my God!
天啊

198
00:13:19,59 --> 00:13:22,32
- There's really money in here. - I know.
- 这里真的有钱 - 这我知道

199
00:13:22,53 --> 00:13:24,23
What are you doing?
你在干什么?

200
00:13:24,43 --> 00:13:28,06
I want you to have it. I don't want it.
我要给你，我不想要

201
00:13:28,27 --> 00:13:31,36
- I have to give you something. - No,you don't
- 不，我得拿东西给你 - 不用了

202
00:13:31,57 --> 00:13:35,17
- Do you want my tinfoil hat? - No,you need that.
- 你要我的锡箔纸帽帽吗? - 不要，因为你需要

203
00:13:35,38 --> 00:13:38,11
- It's okay. Thanks. - Let me do something.
- 不用了，谢谢 - 求你,让我表示我的谢意

204
00:13:39,65 --> 00:13:43,61
I'll tell you what. Buy me a soda and we're even. Okay?
这样吧,你请我喝汽水就扯平了

205
00:13:44,65 --> 00:13:46,35
- Okay. - Okay.
- 好吧 - 好吧

206
00:14:47,78 --> 00:14:49,77
Keep the change.
不用找了

207
00:14:49,98 --> 00:14:51,01
Thanks,Lizzy.
谢谢你，莉兹

208
00:14:51,22 --> 00:14:52,38
Want a pretzel?
你真的不要椒盐卷饼?

209
00:14:52,65 --> 00:14:55,55
- No,I'm fine. Thanks. - See you.
- 不,不用了 - 再见

210
00:15:03,60 --> 00:15:05,86
A thumb?
一个拇指？

211
00:15:07,10 --> 00:15:10,16
I know. There it was, just floating..
我知道.我打开时它就浮在里面

212
00:15:10,37 --> 00:15:13,86
like this tiny little hitchhiker.
像个搭便车的

213
00:15:14,74 --> 00:15:18,77
Maybe it's a contest. Like "collect all five."
或者这是一场竞赛,比如集满五个有奖?

214
00:15:20,01 --> 00:15:22,85
- Does anyone wanna see? - No,thanks!
- 你们想看看吗? - 不用了，谢谢

215
00:15:24,75 --> 00:15:26,34
Don't do that. Come on!
别那样，拜托

216
00:15:26,55 --> 00:15:29,22
It's worse than the thumb.
这比姆指还糟糕

217
00:15:30,46 --> 00:15:33,26
- This is so unfair. - Why is it unfair?
- 这不公平 - 为何不公平?

218
00:15:33,46 --> 00:15:36,26
So I have a flaw! Big deal!
我有缺点行吗?了不起

219
00:15:36,46 --> 00:15:39,09
Joey's knuckle-cracking isn't annoying?
乔依常扳指关节就不惹人厌?

220
00:15:39,30 --> 00:15:41,46
Ross,over-pronouncing every word.
罗斯把每个音发得太清楚

221
00:15:41,67 --> 00:15:47,27
Monica,who snorts when she laughs. I mean,what the hell is that thing?
摩妮卡大笑时的鼻音 搞什么嘛

222
00:15:48,24 --> 00:15:52,68
I accept those flaws. Why can't you accept me for this?
我接受大家所有的缺点 为何大家就不肯接受我的呢?

223
00:15:58,75 --> 00:16:02,95
Does the knuckle-cracking bother everybody,or just him?
扳指关节会惹人厌吗?还是只是他比较烦

224
00:16:05,83 --> 00:16:07,62
I could live without it.
没有它我也能活的下去

225
00:16:10,46 --> 00:16:15,70
Is it a little annoying? Or is it like when Phoebe chews her hair?
我觉得有点点烦? 感觉就和看到菲此咬她的头发时一样?

226
00:16:18,07 --> 00:16:21,20
Don't listen to him. I think it's endearing.
菲此，别介意 我觉得那样很可爱

227
00:16:21,41 --> 00:16:23,64
Oh,you do,do you?
真的?是吗?

228
00:16:29,85 --> 00:16:32,98
There's nothing wrong with speaking correctly.
咬字清晰又不犯法

229
00:16:33,39 --> 00:16:35,95
Indeed there isn't.
没错

230
00:16:38,16 --> 00:16:39,89
I should get back to work.
我该回去工作了

231
00:16:40,09 --> 00:16:43,76
Otherwise someone might get what they ordered.
否则有人就会拿错他们点的东西

232
00:16:45,93 --> 00:16:50,03
The hair comes out and the gloves come off.
头发冒了出来，手套滑落下来 (全都发泄出来了)

233
00:17:04,32 --> 00:17:08,08
Ever go out with a guy your friends really like?
你曾和一个你朋友都喜欢的男人约会吗?

234
00:17:08,29 --> 00:17:10,02
No.
没有

235
00:17:12,39 --> 00:17:15,66
I'm going out with a guy my friends really like.
我在和一个我朋友都喜欢的男人约会

236
00:17:15,86 --> 00:17:18,89
Are we talking about the coyotes here?
我们在谈郊狼吗?

237
00:17:19,10 --> 00:17:22,90
All right! A cow got through.
一头牛居然全身而退

238
00:17:23,64 --> 00:17:24,90
Can you believe it?
你能相信吗?

239
00:17:25,11 --> 00:17:26,77
It's just,you know what?
就像是，你知道吗…

240
00:17:26,97 --> 00:17:29,77
I just don't feel the "thing."
我毫无感觉

241
00:17:29,98 --> 00:17:32,61
They feel the thing. I don't feel it.
而他们却有感觉.我毫无感觉

242
00:17:32,81 --> 00:17:37,61
Honey,you should always feel the thing.
你应该要有感觉

243
00:17:40,25 --> 00:17:43,66
If that's how you feel about the guy, dump him.
如果对他没感觉,就把他甩了

244
00:17:43,86 --> 00:17:47,29
- It's gonna be really hard. - He'll get over it.
- 我知道，但很难 - 没错，但他是大人了,他会熬过去的

245
00:17:47,49 --> 00:17:52,52
No,he'll be fine. It's the other five I'm worried about.
不，他没事.我担心的是其他五人

246
00:17:52,80 --> 00:17:56,86
- Don't you respect your body? - Don't you see what you're doing?
- 难道你不尊重你的身体吗? - 你难道不明白自己自己在做什么吗?

247
00:17:57,07 --> 00:18:01,01
I've had it with your cancer, emphysema and heart disease.
还有你们的癌症肺气肿和心脏病

248
00:18:01,41 --> 00:18:05,61
The bottom line is,smoking is cool, and you know it.
至少抽烟很酷,这点你们也很清楚

249
00:18:09,15 --> 00:18:10,95
Alan wants to speak to you.
钱德，亚伦找你

250
00:18:11,15 --> 00:18:13,35
Really? He does?
真的,他找我?

251
00:18:14,29 --> 00:18:17,02
Hey,buddy! What's up?
老兄，什么事?

252
00:18:18,43 --> 00:18:20,45
She told you about that,huh?
她告诉你了?

253
00:18:21,36 --> 00:18:25,49
Well,yeah. I have one now and then. Well,yeah,now.
对，我偶尔会犯烟瘾 对，现在

254
00:18:26,40 --> 00:18:28,30
It's not that
没那么糟

255
00:18:30,24 --> 00:18:32,17
Well,that's true.
这倒是真的

256
00:18:34,51 --> 00:18:38,71
Gee,you know,no one's ever put it like that before.
天啊，没人这么说过

257
00:18:38,91 --> 00:18:41,51
Well,okay. Thanks.
好的，谢谢

258
00:18:51,33 --> 00:18:53,49
God,he's good.
天啊，他真神

259
00:18:54,16 --> 00:18:57,82
- If only he were a woman. - Yeah.
- 如果他是个女人,那该有多好 - 是的啊

260
00:19:03,07 --> 00:19:04,26
Lamb Chop!
小羊排!

261
00:19:04,47 --> 00:19:07,67
How old is that sock?
那袜子到底有多旧了?

262
00:19:07,98 --> 00:19:12,28
If I had a sock on my hand for 30 years,it'd be talking too.
如果我手上戴着袜子三十年 它也会开始说话

263
00:19:14,18 --> 00:19:18,74
I think it's time to change somebody's nicotine patch.
有人该换尼古丁贴片了

264
00:19:22,29 --> 00:19:25,09
- Where's Joey? - Joey ate my last stick of gum..
- 乔依在哪儿? - 乔依吃了我的最後一片口香糖

265
00:19:25,29 --> 00:19:27,39
so I killed him.
所以我就把他杀了

266
00:19:27,83 --> 00:19:29,96
Do you think that was wrong?
你认为这样不对吗?

267
00:19:31,47 --> 00:19:34,26
- I think he's across the hall. - Thanks.
- 我想他在对面 - 谢谢

268
00:19:34,74 --> 00:19:36,86
There you go.
好啦

269
00:19:37,20 --> 00:19:40,11
I'm alive with pleasure now.
我又重拾快乐的生活

270
00:19:40,31 --> 00:19:44,07
Phoebe,do you want the rest of that Pop-Tart?
菲此，你还想吃那个吗?

271
00:19:45,28 --> 00:19:48,15
Does anyone want the rest of this Pop-Tart?
谁想吃剩下的?

272
00:19:49,65 --> 00:19:51,45
Hey,I might.
我要

273
00:19:51,82 --> 00:19:53,88
I'm sorry.
抱歉

274
00:19:54,09 --> 00:19:58,55
The soda people gave me $7000 for the thumb.
汽水公司那些笨蛋 给我七千元当姆指的补偿金

275
00:19:59,93 --> 00:20:03,16
And on my way over here I stepped in gum.
天啊，七千元别闹了 我回家路上又踩到口香糖

276
00:20:03,83 --> 00:20:06,06
What is up with the universe?
这世界到底怎么了?

277
00:20:06,27 --> 00:20:10,36
- What's going on? - It's just nice when we're together.
- 怎么啦？ - 只是觉得大夥儿在一起很温馨

278
00:20:10,57 --> 00:20:14,06
It's nicer when everyone gets to wear underwear.
如果大家都有穿内裤会更好

279
00:20:24,35 --> 00:20:26,48
Please,guys,we have to talk.
大家，我有话要说

280
00:20:26,69 --> 00:20:29,42
Wait! I'm getting a deja vu.
等等，我有似曾相识的感觉

281
00:20:29,62 --> 00:20:30,75
No,I'm not.
不,好像没有

282
00:20:33,53 --> 00:20:36,50
- We have to talk. - There it is!
- 好吧,我们需要谈谈. - 瞧,来了

283
00:20:39,20 --> 00:20:41,00
Okay,it's about Alan.
是有关亚伦的事

284
00:20:41,20 --> 00:20:45,66
Speaking of which,tell him we're on for the Renaissance Fair.
关于什么，告诉他文艺复兴已经开始了

285
00:20:45,94 --> 00:20:50,21
Before you get into that, there's something you should know.
在此之前，有件事应该让你们知道

286
00:20:50,81 --> 00:20:54,65
There's really no easy way to say this.
真的很难启齿

287
00:20:55,95 --> 00:20:59,21
I've decided to break up with Alan.
我决定和亚伦分手

288
00:21:02,82 --> 00:21:05,49
Is there somebody else?
有第三者?

289
00:21:07,39 --> 00:21:09,29
No,it's just..
没有

290
00:21:09,50 --> 00:21:12,43
you know,things change. People change.
只是世事难料，人都会变

291
00:21:12,63 --> 00:21:15,00
We didn't change.
我们没变

292
00:21:17,24 --> 00:21:20,37
So that's it? It's over?
就这样?结束了?

293
00:21:20,81 --> 00:21:22,90
Just like that?
就这样结束了

294
00:21:24,04 --> 00:21:29,18
You let your guard down. You start to care about someone,and..
放下防御，真心对待一个人…

295
00:21:32,32 --> 00:21:34,48
- I can go on pretending - Okay!
- 我可以继续伪装… - 可以啊

296
00:21:34,69 --> 00:21:35,75
No.
不

297
00:21:35,96 --> 00:21:39,08
That wouldn't be fair to me,Alan, or to you.
这样对我不公平,对亚伦也不公平 对你们大家都不公平

298
00:21:39,29 --> 00:21:41,28
Well,who wants fair?
是吗?谁要公平?

299
00:21:41,50 --> 00:21:45,69
I just want things back,you know, the way they were.
 我只想要回失去的，回到往日

300
00:21:47,67 --> 00:21:51,87
- I'm sorry. - Oh,she's sorry. I feel better.
- 我很抱歉 - 她说抱歉，我舒坦多了

301
00:21:53,14 --> 00:21:54,66
I can't believe this!
我真是不敢相信

302
00:21:54,88 --> 00:21:59,94
With the holidays coming up. I wanted him to meet my family.
 连续假期就要来临了 我要带他去见我的家人

303
00:22:00,78 --> 00:22:03,68
I'll meet someone. There'll be other Alans.
我会找到新欢的，另一个亚伦

304
00:22:03,88 --> 00:22:05,04
Yeah,right!
是呀,另一个

305
00:22:09,89 --> 00:22:13,45
- Are you guys gonna be okay? - We'll be fine.
- 你们不会有事吧? - 我们会好的

306
00:22:13,66 --> 00:22:16,25
We're just gonna need a little time.
我们只是需要一点时间

307
00:22:17,20 --> 00:22:19,39
I understand.
我了解

308
00:22:24,07 --> 00:22:26,54
- Wow. - I'm really sorry.
- Wow - 我真的很抱歉

309
00:22:26,74 --> 00:22:29,87
Yeah,I mean,I'm sorry too.
我也很抱歉

310
00:22:30,08 --> 00:22:33,41
- But I'm a little relieved. - Relieved?
- 我有点松口气了 - 松了一口气?

311
00:22:33,61 --> 00:22:37,28
Yeah,well,I mean, I had a great time with you.
对，我是说我和你在一起很开心

312
00:22:37,82 --> 00:22:40,72
I just can't stand your friends.
只是我受不了你朋友

313
00:22:46,53 --> 00:22:50,33
Remember when we went to Central Park and rented boats?
记得我们到中央公园划船吗?

314
00:22:51,97 --> 00:22:54,16
That was fun.
没错，那很有趣

315
00:22:55,20 --> 00:22:58,14
He could row like a Viking.
他划得就像维京人一样

316
00:23:06,51 --> 00:23:08,88
So how'd it go?
情况如何?

317
00:23:09,38 --> 00:23:11,11
You know.
你知道的

318
00:23:11,32 --> 00:23:13,72
Did he mention us?
他有提到我们吗?

319
00:23:17,72 --> 00:23:20,92
He says he's really gonna miss you guys.
他说他会想念你们的

320
00:23:27,13 --> 00:23:29,66
- Rough day,huh? - You have no idea.
- 悲惨的一天? - 你无法体会

321
00:23:29,87 --> 00:23:31,77
Come here.
过来宝贝

322
00:23:34,78 --> 00:23:37,30
- That's it. I'm getting cigarettes. - No!
- No! - 我受够了，我要抽烟 - 不行…

323
00:23:37,51 --> 00:23:39,81
I don't care! I'm weak!
我管不了那么多了,我投降,我是懦夫

324
00:23:40,01 --> 00:23:41,91
I've gotta have the smoke!
我要抽烟

325
00:23:42,12 --> 00:23:45,81
If you never smoke again, I'll give you $7000.
如果你不再抽烟我就给你七千块

326
00:23:46,02 --> 00:23:47,85
Yeah,all right.
好吧,没问题

327
00:00:00,00 --> 00:00:00,00


328
